sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client / UI BFF
    participant Istio as Istio Gateway<br/>mTLS STRICT
    participant MR as Model Registry<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant DB as MySQL/PostgreSQL<br/>3306/5432 TCP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Controller as ISVC Controller<br/>8081/TCP
    participant KServe as KServe Pod<br/>(init container)
    participant CSI as mr-storage-initializer
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Job as Async Upload Job
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Sigstore as Sigstore<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,DB: Flow 1: Model Registration via REST API
    Client->>Istio: POST /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/registered_models<br/>HTTP
    Istio->>MR: Forward (mTLS STRICT)<br/>Istio AuthorizationPolicy
    MR->>DB: INSERT (MySQL/PostgreSQL protocol)<br/>Username/Password, Optional TLS 1.2+
    DB-->>MR: Result
    MR-->>Istio: 201 Created (JSON)
    Istio-->>Client: Response

    Note over K8sAPI,MR: Flow 2: InferenceService Sync (Controller)
    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch InferenceService events<br/>TLS 1.2+, SA Token
    Controller->>MR: PUT /inference_services<br/>HTTP, Bearer Token
    MR->>DB: UPSERT
    DB-->>MR: Result
    MR-->>Controller: 200 OK
    Controller->>K8sAPI: PATCH InferenceService labels<br/>HTTPS 443, SA Token

    Note over KServe,S3: Flow 3: Model Download via CSI Storage Initializer
    KServe->>CSI: Init container invocation<br/>model-registry:// URI
    CSI->>MR: GET /model_artifacts/{id}<br/>HTTP 8080, No Auth
    MR-->>CSI: Artifact URI (s3://...)
    CSI->>S3: Download model<br/>HTTPS 443, Storage Credentials
    S3-->>CSI: Model artifacts
    CSI-->>KServe: Model ready in volume

    Note over Job,Sigstore: Flow 4: Async Model Upload Job
    Job->>S3: GET source artifacts<br/>HTTPS 443, Source Credentials
    S3-->>Job: Model files
    Job->>OCI: Push model image<br/>HTTPS 443, Registry Credentials
    OCI-->>Job: Push complete
    Job->>Sigstore: Sign model (Fulcio/Rekor/TSA)<br/>HTTPS 443, K8s SA Token (OIDC)
    Sigstore-->>Job: Signature
    Job->>MR: PUT /model_artifacts<br/>HTTP 8080, Bearer Token
    MR->>DB: UPDATE artifact metadata
    DB-->>MR: Result
    MR-->>Job: 200 OK
